      <h1 class="bg-hero__title">A guide to diamonds</h1>
      <p class="bg-hero__lead">A short, plain-spoken guide from the Milman atelier — the things that genuinely matter for beauty in the hand, in the order you should care about them.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="bg-quick">
